Hiddukel is a fat, ugly man-god. He likes coins and wants them more than anything so he uses his red dragons to go get that. Paladine doesn't like him AT ALL!
- Kender Child explaining Krynn mythology</p>
Hiddukel dwells on the 333rd Layer of the+Abyss in a Realm called Broken Scale.</p>
Sources: Dragonlance Adventures, Dragonlance Campaign Setting (Third Edition), On Hallowed Ground